original_title: STARRCAST II: NITRO - 83 Weeks With Eric Bischoff
overview: WCW made history for 83 weeks straight and at the helm of it all - Monday NITRO! There is nobody better suited to tell the tale of NITRO and these 83 weeks than The Man himself - Eric Bischoff!
title: STARRCAST II: NITRO - 83 Weeks With Eric Bischoff
